#

Carrot and Chickpea Salad

10 min
$5
180 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Mediterranean

Course:

Salad

Tags:

SaladHealthyQuick Meal

Description

A refreshing and nutritious salad packed with protein and fiber, perfect for a quick meal!

Ingredients

  • canned chickpeas: 1 can (15 oz)
  • carrots: 2 medium, grated
  • red bell pepper: 1, diced
  • cilantro or parsley: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
